  div.wrapper-inner
    div.row
      div.col-xs-12
        h2.marginless.text--purple
          | We are focused on providing an accessible place for beginner to expert
          | photographers to use.
        hr.short.hr--purple
      div.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        p
          | Let's be real: one of the hardest things about being a photographer in the 
          | Midwest is the supossed lack of photo locations, expecially if you don't 
          | have access to a studio! That's where we come in... for $20/hour you
          | can have your own studio space and meeting room that you can use to take portraits,
          | artisitc shoots, do product photography, and get crazy!
      div.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        p
          | Studio 402 is owned by two Lincoln photographers, Noah Buscher and Amanda Leise,
          | and we know what photographers need to have a sucessful shoot. That's why we provide
          | studio lighting, backdrops, props, equiptment, and, of course, coffee! So what are
