        p
          | We get it that photographers have it hard: you're an artist, manage your
          | own business, and often even end up being a taxi driver for you clients.
          | You can rest easy knowing we're extremely affordable in additon to being
          | completely transparent.
    div.row
      div.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        h2 Per Hour
        h3 $20/hr
        p
          | Need a studio space to snap a few portraits? We got your back. Just block
          | off the time in the studio online and submit payment via PayPal! It's really
          | that easy.
      
      div.col-md-6.col-xs-12
